metadata.name: NrGO Generation I Membership Pass #02
metadata.description:
For our first generation, we decided to focus on the African continent as it is the most exposed region to the adverse effects of climate change despite contributing the least to global warming. The mission will first start in Morocco, as it is one of the leaders in the Renewable Energy Sector.
Note: The transfer of NFT memberships to other wallets will be suspended until the construction of the DAO is finished.
